{"tid":1142060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯想買祖記大巴拿，有C朗幫手","createTime":"2019-05-07T00:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T02:19:27.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"128da7516f5be68a89c1b6de898719a049b849cd","tid":1142060,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"據RMC Sports援引意大利足球市場的報導，曼聯與尤文圖斯已經就迪巴拉的轉會建立了聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n足球市場稱，索爾斯克亞執教的曼聯想要引進這位阿根廷前鋒，並將與尤文圖斯就這筆轉會展開談判。<br />\n<br />\n在克里斯蒂亞諾-羅納爾多加盟尤文圖斯後，迪巴拉不再擔任球隊進攻核心，這使得他在今夏心生去意。"},{"pid":"c8b4e6048449d7aca10572c869b791921e19696f","tid":1142060,"uid":9347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:12:32.000Z","msg":"又買祖記垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccb17d35b7a9f451e1fce96deb52049f578ce4b","tid":1142060,"uid":47496,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"有歐聯唔踢去踢歐霸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d395458f424c845719eb51b88413bcc9a60544c","tid":1142060,"uid":17889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:13:26.000Z","msg":"戴巴拿唔太岩英超風格"},{"pid":"01a7b77974a8a9bedfc52aba5ffc6b504a9829a5","tid":1142060,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"仲有卡雲尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據Paris United的報導，巴黎總監恩里克希望能在今夏出售卡瓦尼，而卡瓦尼希望等到2020年他的合同到期了再離隊。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，很多球隊都在關注卡瓦尼的情況，曼聯就是其中的一家。據悉，索爾斯克亞很欣賞卡瓦尼，他們可能用他來接替可能離隊的盧卡庫，另一方面盧卡庫也被推薦給了巴黎。"},{"pid":"b750b5f7309d84d5dc9c7b74ebe5a782e39ad7f8","tid":1142060,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:15:39.000Z","msg":"唔好攪我啦好麻"},{"pid":"9eb1b87cf7691b6bb7185e75373ca04d4f5f021c","tid":1142060,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b4e6048449d7aca10572c869b791921e19696f","tid":1142060,"uid":9347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"scor